  "page": "Humfrey Bracken",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/50px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/75px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/100px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Humfrey Bracken</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/50px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/75px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/100px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Lord of the Stone Hedge\">Lord of the Stone Hedge</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">Greens</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nThree wives<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Amos_Bracken\" title=\"Amos Bracken\">Amos Bracken</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Raylon_Rivers\" title=\"Raylon Rivers\">Raylon Rivers</a></li><li>Other children<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rogue_Prince\" title=\"The Rogue Prince\">The Rogue Prince</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nChris David Storer</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_1\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Humfrey Bracken</b> was the Lord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Stone Hedge\">Stone Hedge</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a> during the reign of kings <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a>.\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>, Humfrey is portrayed by <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_actors_of_House_of_the_Dragon#Chris_David_Storer.2C_Humfrey_Bracken\" title=\"List of actors of House of the Dragon\">Chris David Storer</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rhbohotds01e04.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rhbohotds01e04.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Bracken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Humfrey hosted Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> when she <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">visited</a> the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">Trident</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_112_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">112&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a> supported the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> when the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a> began, while <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a> declared for the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a>. Humfrey's son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Amos_Bracken\" title=\"Amos Bracken\">Amos Bracken</a>, and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Blackwood\" title=\"Samwell Blackwood\">Samwell Blackwood</a> both died during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Burning_Mill\" title=\"Battle of the Burning Mill\">Battle of the Burning Mill</a>, after which Amos's half-brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raylon_Rivers\" title=\"Raylon Rivers\">Raylon Rivers</a>, led the Bracken survivors back to <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Stone Hedge\">Stone Hedge</a>. In the meantime, however, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a> had <a href=\"/index.php/Storming_of_Stone_Hedge\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Storming of Stone Hedge\">stormed Stone Hedge</a> and captured Humfrey, his remaining children, his third wife, and his lowborn <a href=\"/index.php/Paramour\" title=\"Paramour\">paramour</a>. Raylon surrendered to Daemon to spare his kin's lives.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a> began punishing <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> after the death of his rival, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a>, Humfrey joined the host of blacks led by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Elmo_Tully\" title=\"Elmo Tully\">Elmo Tully</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Bracken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />woman</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font: